title: Fresh apple walnut cake
ingredients: ['375g plain flour', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '3 apples - peeled, cored and sliced', '200g caster sugar', '220g soft brown sugar', '295ml vegetable oil', '2 eggs', '2 teaspoons vanilla extract', '115g chopped walnuts']
